HEADWORD: halobacterium
<hw>halobacterium</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>halobacteria</plw> <pr>(?)</pr>, or
<plw>halobacters</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <def>Any halophilic bacterium
